circulSupHov: The sum of liquid GNS tokens including released vesting allocations and cumulative block emissions.
comPoolHov: Amount of GNS accumulated in the Community Pool from Emissions.
dailyBlockHov: Number of newly minted GNS tokens per block.
holdersHov: Number of accounts with at least 1 xGNS.
totalStakedHov: Amount of GNS in LPs being staked.
totalSupHov: The total supply of GNS tokens is 1,000,000,000 GNS.
totalXGNS: Total amount of xGNS currently issued through GNS-GNOT staking.
